                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p>Wat kunnen we leren van dit experiment?</p>\n<p class=\"text-align-center\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/apzXGEbZht0\" width=\"500\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n"
