                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<h2><strong>Amerika</strong></h2>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/U3ay0Oysrlc\" width=\"500\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><strong>Japan</strong></h2>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NoXczyACgyo\" width=\"500\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<h2><strong>Nederland</strong></h2>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-QhsdJzsc-Q\" width=\"500\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><strong>Mexico</strong></h2>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AXxG1esGVcw\" width=\"500\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><strong>Argentini\u00eb</strong></h2>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QBlj6hjbyc0\" width=\"500\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<h2><strong>Zuid-Afrika</strong></h2>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_RvIj6FjAT4\" width=\"400\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<h2><strong>Taiwan en China</strong></h2>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YAo11nHWJDE\" width=\"500\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n<h2><strong>Rusland</strong></h2>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wqH0NSB3XNs\" width=\"500\" class=\"video-item\"/></p>\n"
                }
            ],
            "sections": [
                {
                    "reference": {
                        "value": "3253028"
                    },
                    "heading": {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "content": "Extra opdracht",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p>Met dit spel leer je los te komen van een automatische reactie. Het werkt als volgt:</p>\n<p>Je staat met elkaar in een kring. E\u00e9n iemand staat in het midden. Deze stapt op iemand af en zegt 'Zeg jij daar!' met een vooraf gekozen emotie. De ander herhaalt deze zin maar dan met precies een tegenovergestelde emotie.</p>\n<p>Dus blij - verdrietig, boos - vriendelijk, enzovoort.</p>\n<p class=\"text-align-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/f/f191b836130983383dc80c7e9b974705377a98f5.jpg\" class=\"height-388-pixels width-690-pixels\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                        }
